The point $P$ marks an irrational number. Which number is it?
[tikz]
\begin{tikzpicture}
\draw[{Stealth}-{Stealth}] (-0.4,0)--(6.4,0);
\foreach \x in {0,1,2,3,4} {\draw (1.5*\x,0.12)--(1.5*\x,-0.12); \node[below] at (1.5*\x,-0.12) {$\x$};}
\foreach \x in {0.5,1.5,2.5,3.5} {\draw (1.5*\x,0.07)--(1.5*\x,-0.07);}
\fill (2.12,0) circle (2.2pt);
\node[above] at (2.12,0.18) {$P$};
\end{tikzpicture}
[/tikz]

